commitResults.messageTitle: Modified main method to echo commands entered by the user, and exits program when the user types the command "bye".
Added method addTasks(String Task) to store text entered by user.
commitResults.messageBody: Added method printTasks() to display all tasks entered by user when requested using command  "list".

commitResults.messageTitle: Added the ability to mark tasks as done or not done using markTask(String input).
commitResults.messageBody:
Added class Task to encapsulate functionality of a task.

(cherry picked from commit 1cffefbfd26873836546ea41b69b56280ac26413)

commitResults.messageTitle: Adjusted code to comply with given coding standard.
Added support for tracking 3 types of tasks: ToDo, Deadline, Event extending Task Class.
commitResults.messageBody: Encapsulate interaction with user in UserInterface Class and input parsing of input in Parser for better abstraction.

commitResults.messageTitle: Modified runtest.bat to work with current directory to perform automated text UI testing.
Gave meaningful name to temporary variables.
Handled error using InvalidCommand and InvalidTaskNumber exceptions, added try catch to catch invalid task description formatting.
Organised classes into Prune, Exceptions, Tasks packages.
Changed Task array type to ArrayList, added support for deleting tasks from list.
Added saving of most updated task list into saved_tasks.txt and ability to load the data on start up.
Removed write funcs comments in Parser.
Create saved_tasks.txt in folder data if file does not exist, relative to root.
Extracted out classes Ui, Storage, TaskList. Same features as the previous commit.
Fixed saving tasks after every command.
